title: Cedars
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small cafe with an open kitchen. At least two vegan and two vegetarian specials are available daily as well as the daily menu, and desserts including a vegan choice. Soup is always vegan, and a vegetarian and vegan version of an English fried breakfast is available all day, and cooked in separate fryers. Wi-fi.
